{"tid":927866,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★特價未？】將軍澳天晉3人染退伍軍人病　2男病人危殆","createTime":"2018-12-04T12:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T13:13:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"53b7106227bc8e7b23bc24cca32a019271a225e5","tid":927866,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:28:19.000Z","msg":"將軍澳天晉IIIA爆發退伍軍人病，累計三人中招，其中兩名男病人情況危殆，女病人則穩定。新增一宗社區感染的退伍軍人病個案，69歲男病人有長期病患，居於天晉IIIA 3A座，其樣本細菌的基因分析仍在進行中；該宗為今年第100宗退伍軍人病個案。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心上周一(11月26日)公布兩宗社區感染的退伍軍人病個案，涉及一名61歲男病人及一名76歲女病人，前者居於天晉IIIA，後者則常到該屋苑照顧家人。從兩人呼吸道樣本培養出的嗜肺性退伍軍人桿菌血清1型菌株進行基因分析，發現基因序列型相同。<br />\n<br />\n流行病學調查發現，<span style=\"color: red;\">三人於潛伏期內沒有外遊，但潛伏期內分別居於或曾到天晉IIIA</span>。防護中心已從該屋苑可能感染源頭，分別為天晉IIIA主入口噴水池和2和3座之間的瀑布，採集水樣本化驗。作為預防措施，該屋苑管理公司已暫停上述噴水池和瀑布的運作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181204/bkn-20181204191209869-1204_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181204%2Fbkn-20181204191209869-1204_00822_001.html&d=wy78JA13ImWpYiwIp9yh84M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=c8d6f34f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181204/bkn-20181204191209869-1204_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4f793186146456f70c80db1252e303708d8107f7","tid":927866,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181204/photo/bkn-20181204191209869-1204_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181204201457\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181204%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181204191209869-1204_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181204201457&h=18d636a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfbd747b29d7a577d4dd58aa26548cc4accafe50","tid":927866,"uid":14739,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:02:35.000Z","msg":"公屋是福地"},{"pid":"0992c0f03ff6e075f0ff40f0c8dee86345871643","tid":927866,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dfbd747b29d7a577d4dd58aa26548cc4accafe50","tid":927866,"uid":14739,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:02:35.000Z","msg":"公屋是福地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T13:13:21.000Z","msg":"有鉛水"}]}